When heading westbound on Gatlin Blvd. you will have to make a U-turn at SW Brighton St. (the first left turn) to enter Gatlin Commons.
As an alternative to a U-turn, you can go south on Port St. Lucie Blvd. through the intersection and make your first right-hand turn onto SW Castaneda Lane, then another right onto SW Brighton St.
The entrance is between SW Brighton St. and the Circle K, which is on the southwest corner of Gatlin and Port St Lucie Blvd.
FINE FOOD. GOOD SERVICE. FRIENDLY ATMOSPHERE.

City Limits Events
Here at City Limits, we offer a range of events to suit every taste.
From live sports events to themed parties, there’s always something happening at our sports bar. We’re the perfect place to catch the big game with friends, enjoy a night out on the town, or celebrate a special occasion.
Our events calendar is packed with exciting events throughout the year, so be sure to check back often for updates. We also offer a variety of specials on food and drinks, so you can enjoy your time at City Limits without breaking the bank.
In addition to our events, we also offer a variety of other amenities to make your visit even more enjoyable. We have a full bar with a wide selection of beers, wines, and spirits, as well as a delicious menu of pub fare. We also have a large outdoor patio where you can enjoy the fresh air and sunshine.
So whether you’re looking for a fun night out with friends or a place to watch the game, City Limits is the perfect place for you. We look forward to seeing you soon!
